Interface ApplicationGatewayProbe.UpdateStages.WithHealthyHttpResponseStatusCodeRanges

    public static interface ApplicationGatewayProbe.UpdateStages.WithHealthyHttpResponseStatusCodeRanges
    The stage of an application gateway probe update allowing to specify healthy HTTP response status code ranges.
